     intellectual property laws
   - You will NOT list counterfeit, replica, or unauthorized items
   - You will NOT infringe on copyrights, trademarks, or patents
   - You will obtain proper authorization for branded merchandise

2. FACEBOOK COMMERCE POLICIES COMPLIANCE
   - You must comply with Meta's Commerce Policies and Community Standards
   - You will NOT list prohibited items including but not limited to:
     * Alcohol and tobacco products
     * Weapons, ammunition, and explosives
     * Adult products and services
     * Drugs and drug paraphernalia
     * Animals and endangered species
     * Healthcare items (prescription drugs, medical devices)
     * Recalled or illegal products
     * Services (non-physical items)
     * Digital products and subscriptions
     * Hazardous materials

3. CONTENT ACCURACY & AUTHENTICITY
   - All product descriptions must be accurate and truthful
   - All images must represent the actual item being sold
   - Pricing must be clearly stated and accurate
   - You will not engage in misleading or deceptive practices

4. PLATFORM TERMS OF SERVICE
   - You must comply with Facebook Marketplace Terms of Service
   - You must comply with Meta Platform Terms
   - Violation of platform policies may result in account suspension or ban

5. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY
